snippet.title: Legacy | WWE 2K24 Official Gameplay Trailer | 2K
snippet.description:
The story’s not finished. Take your first look at WWE 2K24’s all-new match types, environments, Superstars and more, including the 2K Showcase… of the Immortals.

Celebrate Forty Years of WrestleMania with new match types, updated gameplay, and more. Available March 8, 2024.

Pre-order #WWE2K24 now: https://wwe.2k.com/2k24/buy/
